Engineering Decision Records (EDRs)
Purpose

This document records every significant engineering decision made during the development of Project Disc.

The goal is to preserve not only what decisions were made, but why they were made.

Each decision should include:

Context
Decision
Alternatives considered
Reasoning
Consequences
Status

Future contributors should be able to understand the evolution of Project Disc without relying on conversations, memory, or assumptions.

